## Synopsis

Practical 2 of Fundamentals of Programming COMP1005/5005

## Contents

README - readme file for Practical 2

File 1: strings1.py - Read in a string and print it in reverse using a loop and a method call

File 2: strings2.py - Read in a string and print it in reverse using a loop and slicing

File 3: bucket1.py - use a python list for items in a bucket list

File 4: bucket2.py - bucket list builder

File 5: assorted.py - selecting random biscuits from a pack

File 6: darts.py - calculating Pi using the Method of Darts

File 7: cointoss.py - simulate tossing a coin multiple times

File 8: randomTest.py - testing out random numbers in python

## Dependencies

none

